tings":{"accordion_heading":"Product Information and Usage","heading_style":"font-heading","accordion_text":"<p><strong>How to use?<\/strong><\/p><p>Take 1-2 capsules 30-60 minutes before you want to feel the effect. Ideal before a meeting, during an energy dip, or prior to a workout. 1 capsule contains 99 mg of caffeine.<strong><br\/><br\/>Food Supplement\/Kosttillskott\/Kosttillskudd<\/strong><\/p><p>EN: 60 capsules, 30 doses\/days<br\/>SE: 60 kapslar, 30 doser\/dagar<br\/><br\/><strong>Recommended daily dose\/Rekommenderad daglig dos<\/strong><\/p><p>EN: 1-2 capsules per day.<br\/>SE: 1-2 kapslar per dag.<\/p><p>Produkten bör inte användas som ersättning för en varierad kost. Den rekommenderade dagliga dosen bör inte överskridas. Förvaras oåtkomligt för små barn. Kosttillskott bör inte användas som ett alternativ till en balanserad och varierad kost samt en hälsosam livsstil.<\/p>","accordion_page":"","padding_bottom":20}},"a42f4e7d-6a8d-42a4-80af-29ec3b3b52d9":{"type":"feature","disabled":true,"settings":{"icon_name":"support","icon_width":25,"title":"Need help with sizing?","text":"<p>This content type will accept <strong>rich text<\/strong> to help with adding styles and links to additional pages or content. Use this to add supplementary information to help your buyers.<\/p>","bg_color":"#f7f9fa","text_color":"#000000","padding_bottom":20}},"feature_qMXybi":{"type":"feature","disabled":true,"settings":{"icon_name":"none","icon_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2024-02-28_at_14.56_1.png","icon_width":50,"title":"Used by Li Karlsén","text":"<p>The Nordic free dive champion Li Karlsén is the co-founder, maker, and user of all BKM supplements. Her expertise and dedication ensure that every product meets the highest standards of quality and performance.<\/p>","bg_color":"#f7f9fa","text_color":"#000000","padding_bottom":20}},"upsell_PCiGQC":{"type":"upsell","settings":{"product_list":["life-nad"],"padding_bottom":20}}},"block_order":["klaviyo_reviews_avera