"","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--solid","button_size":"btn--medium","enable_slider_mobile":false,"padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"overlapping-images-0":{"type":"section-overlapping-images","disabled":true,"settings":{"text_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","images_width":750,"images_offset":60,"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/bkm_ultra_focused.jpg","image_link_1":"","image_link_2":"","hide_image_2":false,"title":"<p>Focus and energy<\/p>","heading_highlight_type":"highlight","highlight_color":"#0a2240","highlight_text_color":"#ffffff","description":"<p><strong>Supports sustained energy levels:<\/strong><br\/>The combination of Guarana and Yerba Mate provides natural sources of caffeine, which are known to help maintain energy levels throughout the day. Unlike synthetic stimulants, these ingredients offer a more balanced and sustained release of energy, helping you stay active and alert without the typical crashes associated with other energy products.<\/p><p><strong>Enhances focus and mental clarity:<\/strong><br\/>Ginseng extract and Lion's Mane have been traditionally used to support mental clarity and concentration. Ginseng is known for its adaptogenic properties, which help the body adapt to stress and support cognitive function. Lion's Mane, a renowned medicinal mushroom, is believed to support brain health by promoting the production of nerve growth factors.<\/p><p><strong>Helps maintain cognitive function:<\/strong><br\/>Cordyceps Powder and Piperine from black pepper extract are included for their supportive roles in cognitive health. Cordyceps has been used in traditional medicine to support vitality and overall well-being, which can contribute to better cognitive function. Piperine enhances the bioavailability of other ingredients, ensuring that your body can absorb and utilize them more effectively.<\/p>","heading_size":100,"button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--solid","button_size":"btn--small","video_text":"","video_link":"","bg_color_secondary":false,"gradient":"","animation":"horizontal","animation_intensity":50,"width":"wrapper--full-padded","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"section_image_with_text_mKzLcp":{"type":"section-image-with-text","settings":{"section_height":"six-fifty-height","layout":"inline","image_location":"left","image_width":"standard","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/bkm_ultra_focused.jpg","subheading":"","title":"<p>When do you want to be ultra focused?<\/p>","heading_highlight_type":"circle","highlight_color":"#d43747","highlight_text_color":"#000000","heading_size":130,"content":"<h5><strong>Sport<\/strong><\/h5><p>When you're training hard or competing, distractions are the last thing you need. With natural caffeine and mushroom extracts, BKM Ultra Focused delivers sustained energy and sharp mental clarity to keep you in the zone longer, without the crash.<\/p><p>‎ <\/p><h5><strong>Work<\/strong><\/h5><p>Need to power through back-to-back meetings, endless emails, or a critical deadline? Ultra Focused gives you the boost you need with ingredients that fight brain fog and help maintain laser-like focus, so you can perform at your best, all day.<\/p><p>‎ <\/p><h5><strong>Study<\/strong><\/h5><p>Staying on top of your studies can be tough, but BKM Ultra Focused helps you stay energized and clear-headed. Whether cramming for exams or deep into research, you’ll experience sharper concentration and longer-lasting mental focus to get the job done right.<\/p>","text_alignment":"left","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--solid","button_size":"btn--small","video_link":"","text_color":"text-dark","bg_color":"","gradient":"","section_width":"wrapper","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"section_text_RQVUM4":{"type":"section-text","blocks":{"heading_3Q87aT":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"<p>Proven by Performers, Approved by Expe